\id OBA Matupi Chin Standard Bible 
\h OBADIAH 
\toc1 OBADIAH 
\toc2 Obadiah 
\toc3 Oba 
\mt1 OBADIAH  
\mt2 (The Book of Obadiah)  
\is1 Obadiah Cabu Kawng  
\im Obadiah he Tuipuei Duek tuithim kah Edom soah laitloeknah a thui. Edom he Isaak casak Esau cadil rhoek ni. Isau neh Jakop he boeina rhoi ni. Esau he a manuca Judah soah kopoek a sang la a khueh dongah ni Pathen a thin a toek. Babylonian caem loh Jerusalem te 586 \sc b.c.\sc* ah a phae ha tah Edom loh a omtoem tih Judah khopuei rhoek te a hul uh. Te dongah Edom ngawn tah rheprhep cungku pawn ni. Israel te ram koep a thoh pah ni a ti.  
\iot Sawt Yoeinah  
\io1 I. Edom cungkunah \ior 1-9\ior*  
\io2 A. Hmuencak tim ni \ior 1-4\ior*  
\io2 B. A kueh tawn ung ni \ior 5-9\ior*  
\io1 II. Edom a cungku timanh \ior 10-14\ior*  
\io1 III. Edom poci tangkik \ior 15-21\ior*  
\io2 A. Tholh soah laitloeknah \ior 15-16\ior*  
\io2 B. Tholh lamloh khangnah \ior 17-20\ior*  
\io2 C. Ram tho nah \ior 21\ior*  
\c 1  
\s1 Edom soah Laitloeknah  
\p
